{"tid":927400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲「富二代」一夜情後：我有愛滋　44歲熟女當場痛哭","createTime":"2018-12-04T06:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T11:36:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd464fa4a2e2c7e3dab57c592ae2a832c9ee56b3","tid":927400,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"中國浙江一名44歲的女子，日前在上海認識一名22歲的男子，兩人當晚馬上發生性關係，也一起到杭州遊玩。沒想到，就在女子借了男子7500元人民幣（約3.34萬元台幣）後，對方突然不告而別。後來女子找到他，向他討債時，男子卻稱自己有愛滋病，嚇得女子當場痛哭。<br />\n《梨視頻》報導，上周二（27日）下午約1時，原籍四川、從事服務生工作的女子，杭州火車東站與男子拉扯，並大喊：「你不要走，你還我錢」，吸引路人圍觀。女子表示，她與男子是透過社交網站認識，雙方相處、一起生活3天後，她對男方印象不錯。男子還向她聲稱，在廣州擁有千萬家產，日後要把旗下飯店交給她管理。可是不久後，男子就以「他公司現在差一點錢」為由，向她借了7500元，承諾月底會還，但事後卻企圖逃走。<br />\n男子則向警方供稱，自己根本身無分文，「借給朋友了，已經沒了」，加上不堪女方糾纏、煩擾，所以在還了4200元後（約1.87萬元台幣）後，乾脆聲稱自己有愛滋病。警方認為，男子的愛滋病「只是心情不爽，想嚇唬對方」，所以要他寫在借據後，就放他離開。對此，女子揚言，會透過法律途徑追討款項。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181204/640_f964a1c22352b0ce5be6dd1149332c86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181204%2F640_f964a1c22352b0ce5be6dd1149332c86.jpg&h=81d93df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181204/640_fc1447d9b58c232b1f2203a7e1a9d5d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181204%2F640_fc1447d9b58c232b1f2203a7e1a9d5d8.jpg&h=90f12730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181204/640_9db845d93ce148c16f77932030a814af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181204%2F640_9db845d93ce148c16f77932030a814af.jpg&h=db51399c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181204/640_6283394bed12332d22e046ae3858c905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181204%2F640_6283394bed12332d22e046ae3858c905.jpg&h=5bacc69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181204/640_962928f7e4a9d2e8633ce17db3a92d82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181204%2F640_962928f7e4a9d2e8633ce17db3a92d82.jpg&h=3a6f91a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181204/640_1e6eb49c9dc2d224e290ce1e95e43455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181204%2F640_1e6eb49c9dc2d224e290ce1e95e43455.jpg&h=95bf2524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181204/1477728/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181204%2F1477728%2F&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9a0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=49464c9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181204%2F1477728%2F&h=57534b99\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181204/1477728/</a>"},{"pid":"b56b0834685d7e69122e662cda9b75e0cf9a30c2","tid":927400,"uid":51932,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"44，又唔係富婆，諗太多喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db8476bfd876112be9c9823adc14211c1f8a958","tid":927400,"uid":133528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1780145a5a402b4b6f727b4b0d498ff5ef37aa9","tid":927400,"uid":3195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"有錢人公司爭少少錢會係爭7500咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係發夢發太早"},{"pid":"e60f586695d12055180346987e44473af8d8e1f6","tid":927400,"uid":42487,"like":